milestone: (current milestone is "marvin", also "wishlist" can be used)
  https://github.com/zerovm/zerovm/issues?milestone=21&page=1&state=open

tag "FIX" should be used. the bug severity can be denoted with one of "VALUE+",
"VALUE++" or "VALUE+++" tags

